TextBody:
Hello,

We will share them with you.
Just let us know the current Epp server version you have.

If your version if as indicated on the ticket(5930) you will need the patches below.
Before updating, please create a VM snapshot of on the environment to have a sefe point to return to.
These can be added from "Dashboard > Live Update > Offline Patch Uploader".
Each patch will need to be added one at a time and you need to confirm the previous is applied before adding the next one.

Epp 5.9.3.0 to Epp 5.9.4.0
https://download.endpointprotector.com/offline_patches/EPP00656940.tar.gz  
Epp 5.9.4.0 to Epp 5.9.4.1
https://download.endpointprotector.com/offline_patches/EPP500665941.tar.gz

Kind regards
